{"tid":1853639,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聯合缺罩 院方拒醫護取用","createTime":"2020-01-31T05:54:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T10:23:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f5b28f409bfb62fbef983e48fba0369607e7b35c","tid":1853639,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T05:54:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200131/JEZXMJ53VPDUIC3SMV3CEM2JPE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200131%2FJEZXMJ53VPDUIC3SMV3CEM2JPE%2F&d=7U4Tv3rjd6zAHDU%2B6DwikxvMbnGxJ%2B6Vh8biNj9iadw%3D&h=e1e20141\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200131%2FJEZXMJ53VPDUIC3SMV3CEM2JPE%2F&h=db556f3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200131/JEZXMJ53VPDUIC3SMV3CEM2JPE/</a><br />\n<br />\n聯合缺罩 院方拒醫護取用<br />\n<br />\n大量病人於高危病房接受治療，不少公院都抽調其他部門人手支援。投訴人稱自己在人手編制中不屬於高危病房，只是近日到有關病房支援時，向所屬部門提交醫生紙，欲取用一款須有醫療證明的防敏感口罩時，仍被拒絕。他批評院方不積極向醫護人員提供防疫裝備，更形容院方態度有如「驚你偷」，忽視同事真正需要。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：編入Dirty Team 伊院ICU四護士劈炮<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200131/large/1580403104_03c9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200131%2Flarge%2F1580403104_03c9.gif&h=fbb0a3ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前線醫護人員投訴聯合醫院出現口罩荒，醫護上班時無法取用口罩。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n診所鬧口罩荒或停診<br />\n<br />\n醫管局回覆指，恒常機制預留3個月個人防護裝備存量作緊急使用，月初已加快購置個人防護裝備，並於最近將儲備目標提升至6個月。雖然使用量在過去一星期後顯著上升，但現時各公院仍有足夠保護裝備供醫護人員使用。<br />\n<br />\n此外，香港醫學會會長何仲平昨日在一個電台節目上表示，近日接獲多間私家診所醫生求助，稱現時診所出現口罩短缺問題，估計大部份診所存貨只能應付一至兩星期。若再無補貨，私家診所或需停診。他已聯絡食衞局，希望局方可先撥出數百盒口罩，讓私家診所繼續營業，但局方暫時未有回覆；又重申若私家診所停診，病人將無可避免要到公院急症室求醫，屆時將會加重醫院和醫護人員負擔。<br />\n<br />\n■記者何家朗 張文鈴"},{"pid":"8730ea35c13ab240befd5e1e52aa3febc2ca5dd8","tid":1853639,"uid":321618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T05:56:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">抗疫不忘抗爭</span><br />\n希望大家幫p牌推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n解答到 國際關係 海洋法庭制裁警暴<br />\n呢啲議題 <br />\n唔好比肺炎spin開左 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我地仲未光復到香港！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n沈旭暉高汁分析 點光復香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1853544\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1853544</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ad50694911363789293421cd34742ffd948b041d","tid":1853639,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T05:57:09.000Z","msg":"差人大把"},{"pid":"471ee9a322f9074d517d78110a3f9faa44b12f5b","tid":1853639,"uid":105773,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T06:03:34.000Z","msg":"冇口罩罷工啦"},{"pid":"43e6eac7e6672c54580ec6593044a6116276c9ab","tid":1853639,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T06:08:20.000Z","msg":"冇罩就罷<br />\n有罩都罷"},{"pid":"673f9ddc03264d29cde772a187bdf4f4d6bbf030","tid":1853639,"uid":18895,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T06:09:31.000Z","msg":"班狗係門口就full gear<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"880d427ad07bc3fdb799616b36aaa024c3aecb3f","tid":1853639,"uid":65074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T06:54:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請醫管局解釋<br />\n點解警察可以有全套保護裝備<br />\n出現係醫院但唔幫手救人</span>"},{"pid":"6a81f699eae9b9325213d05efce5a14327f7baa8","tid":1853639,"uid":27605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T06:59:44.000Z","msg":"無罩咪唔返工"},{"pid":"4004a29f07af95105bf6a42078f49e30893a94a9","tid":1853639,"uid":257622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:06:25.000Z","msg":"無口罩再無借口返工"},{"pid":"076ba91bb37fe174578573e6de820bc536f8b91a","tid":1853639,"uid":267600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite